text: Welcoming and stylish, the Main Dining Room – lined with leather banquettes and a curated
photography collection – is the ideal setting for weekday business lunches, intimate dinners or
lively evenings with friends. On weekends, this elegant room can be transformed into a versatile
event space. Enjoy drinks and the bar menu in our intimate restaurant bar, or head to our larger
rooftop bar. Cigars and cognac served!
